{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I went-- one night I went out with a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We went and hoped we would not see anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we got to a bathroom, which was not locked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we went into that bathroom and jumped into the tub, the two of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And it was the most glorious experience I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But anyhow, they-- the British, there were-- I don't remember how many police were with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was mainly Palestine, I think only Palestine police, who were sort of guarding us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they were really very mean, most of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They, for instance, for the first week or so, they, in-- in spite of the ship being huge and empty apart from us, they crowded us together in certain areas.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And they gave the men and women an open latrine together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for the first three or four days, it was terrible, honest to god.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think most of the people got constipated because they didn't want to go to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And only after three or four days, they finally allowed a curtain between the two sides.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they-- you know, it was-- that was unnecessary, what they did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess they wanted to show us you were  bad boys and girls, so we got to punish you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After about four or five days, it got a little better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they allowed us to go on deck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was able to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The food was really quite good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But most of us didn't feel like eating.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most-- we were really pretty down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I know I was sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had a fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a terrible cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
